2
00:00:02.190 --> 00:00:05.110
Hey! You got oshiruko all over me!

3
00:00:05.110 --> 00:00:06.950
That stuff ain't fit to eat!

4
00:00:06.950 --> 00:00:08.740
Might as well cover yourself in it!

5
00:00:10.490 --> 00:00:12.620
Bring out more soup!

6
00:00:12.620 --> 00:00:14.290
Let's have a food fight!

7
00:00:14.290 --> 00:00:16.450
Spill it all!

8
00:00:22.960 --> 00:00:25.090
Why?!

9
00:00:25.090 --> 00:00:28.050
What the hell's wrong with you idiots?!

10
00:00:28.470 --> 00:00:31.430
Why do you get all this food?!

11
00:00:34.130 --> 00:00:37.000
Open up the borderless map, then

12
00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:40.200
Head for that unknown edge of the ocean

13
00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:44.590
LET’S SAIL ON right now, hoist your sails up high

14
00:00:44.590 --> 00:00:47.580
Riding on the wind

15
00:00:52.710 --> 00:00:56.920
DON’T GIVE UP, it’s time to finish what we started

16
00:00:57.110 --> 00:00:59.890
So don't you grow disheartened

17
00:01:00.200 --> 00:01:03.650
Laugh the tears away through the storm

18
00:01:03.850 --> 00:01:08.080
SHOUT IT OUT, when you feel down always remember

19
00:01:08.420 --> 00:01:10.680
That’s what your friends are there for

20
00:01:10.710 --> 00:01:12.840
Y’know there’s no point in fronting,

21
00:01:12.840 --> 00:01:16.760
your crew will always have your back

22
00:01:17.130 --> 00:01:20.860
Even in the face of utter darkness

23
00:01:21.090 --> 00:01:23.850
C’mon, BRAVE IT OUT We’ll be alright

24
00:01:24.150 --> 00:01:27.640
Together you know that we’ll never lose a fight

25
00:01:27.860 --> 00:01:30.630
Open up the borderless map, then

26
00:01:30.650 --> 00:01:33.490
Head for that unknown edge of the ocean

27
00:01:33.790 --> 00:01:38.070
All great journeys starts with a single step

28
00:01:38.140 --> 00:01:39.080
DREAMIN’ ON

29
00:01:39.080 --> 00:01:41.860
Open up the borderless map, then

30
00:01:41.860 --> 00:01:44.600
Raise the flag we swore to defend

31
00:01:44.750 --> 00:01:47.490
We’ll never stop until we’ve reached the top

32
00:01:47.560 --> 00:01:51.960
Just be true to yourself until the end

33
00:01:52.090 --> 00:01:56.800
Set sail and grab it, DREAMIN ON

34
00:02:05.770 --> 00:02:07.940
<b>Battle Music</b>

35
00:02:16.990 --> 00:02:18.950
What's he doing?!

36
00:02:18.950 --> 00:02:21.750
Is red bean soup that good?!

37
00:02:27.710 --> 00:02:30.460
Yeah, it's delicious.

38
00:02:30.460 --> 00:02:32.800
Nothing else even comes close.

39
00:02:41.520 --> 00:02:42.520
So how come...

40
00:02:42.520 --> 00:02:46.480
you guys get to waste it
while Tama goes hungry?!

41
00:03:05.370 --> 00:03:07.750
Gum-Gum...

42
00:03:09.040 --> 00:03:11.750
Elephant Gun!

43
00:03:37.280 --> 00:03:38.990
Captain, look!

44
00:03:43.330 --> 00:03:44.580
It's Straw Hat!

45
00:03:44.580 --> 00:03:47.250
What does that moron think he's doing?!

46
00:03:47.250 --> 00:03:52.880
We disguised ourselves to sneak
through the banquet hall...

47
00:03:52.880 --> 00:03:55.090
Oh, well...

48
00:03:55.090 --> 00:03:55.920
Kid?

49
00:03:55.920 --> 00:03:57.380
Leave him!

50
00:03:57.380 --> 00:04:02.850
While they're focused on
that idiot, we'll slip right by.

51
00:04:12.730 --> 00:04:14.150
What the...?!

52
00:04:44.010 --> 00:04:45.730
Seriously...

53
00:04:46.770 --> 00:04:48.940
You just had to cause a scene!

54
00:04:50.980 --> 00:04:54.320
I made a beeline for the source...

55
00:04:55.730 --> 00:04:58.240
but you've already ruined everything!

56
00:04:58.670 --> 00:05:03.160
Why the hell can't you just sneak in quietly?!

57
00:05:03.160 --> 00:05:04.700
Really?

58
00:05:04.700 --> 00:05:07.500
Does he hear himself right now?

59
00:05:11.290 --> 00:05:13.670
These jerks had it coming!

60
00:05:15.880 --> 00:05:19.050
They were dumping oshiruko for fun!

61
00:05:19.800 --> 00:05:21.180
Oshiruko?!

62
00:05:21.180 --> 00:05:25.510
This soup is so delicious!

63
00:05:26.930 --> 00:05:30.180
In that case, I'll cut them to ribbons!

64
00:05:36.770 --> 00:05:38.900
What kind of surprise is this?

65
00:05:41.860 --> 00:05:43.870
Oshiruko?

66
00:05:43.870 --> 00:05:45.660
Why would that set them off?

67
00:05:46.410 --> 00:05:48.120
Those guys are hopeless.

68
00:05:48.120 --> 00:05:49.700
I can't work with them.

69
00:05:50.870 --> 00:05:53.670
Man, we really stepped in it.

70
00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:58.880
But it's not time to start the battle yet.

71
00:05:58.880 --> 00:06:02.840
I know, but they haven't
figured out who we are yet.

72
00:06:03.260 --> 00:06:05.260
So... Happy now?

73
00:06:05.800 --> 00:06:06.640
Yeah!

74
00:06:07.260 --> 00:06:08.510
Then...

75
00:06:08.510 --> 00:06:09.810
let's beat it!

76
00:06:09.810 --> 00:06:10.730
Okay!

77
00:06:10.730 --> 00:06:12.520
They're making a run for it!

78
00:06:15.150 --> 00:06:16.900
Catch them!

79
00:06:17.360 --> 00:06:18.980
Hey, now...

80
00:06:18.980 --> 00:06:21.190
What's with all the commotion?

81
00:06:25.410 --> 00:06:26.780
Don't tell me...

82
00:06:26.780 --> 00:06:28.200
Are they...?

83
00:06:36.170 --> 00:06:38.040
A-pow-pow! Yo, check it out!

84
00:06:39.420 --> 00:06:43.010
Yo, Queen! I got the scoop
of the century! It'll blow you away!

85
00:06:43.010 --> 00:06:44.220
So listen up, okay?!

86
00:06:44.220 --> 00:06:45.750
Okay, Apoo!

87
00:06:45.750 --> 00:06:46.890
Apoo! Apoo!

88
00:06:46.890 --> 00:06:49.100
Don't be an ass! Share the news with the class!

89
00:06:49.100 --> 00:06:52.060
Brother Apoo! Gimme a nice rhyme, 'poo!

90
00:06:53.730 --> 00:06:55.440
That voice...

91
00:06:57.020 --> 00:06:58.360
Check it out!

92
00:06:58.360 --> 00:07:02.860
Udon's labor camps? That's your domain!
Trying to break out? It'll be in vain!

93
00:07:04.610 --> 00:07:07.160
Once you're inside, you're trapped like a rat!

94
00:07:09.830 --> 00:07:12.160
But check out those two!
What's up with that?!

95
00:07:16.290 --> 00:07:17.460
Oh, should we fight?

96
00:07:19.960 --> 00:07:22.670
Now that I look closely at that duo raising hell,

97
00:07:22.670 --> 00:07:25.300
those jailbreakers down
there are ringing a bell!

98
00:07:32.520 --> 00:07:33.720
No way!

99
00:07:49.200 --> 00:07:51.580
Yes way! You ain't trippin', yo!

100
00:07:56.000 --> 00:08:00.710
It's Straw Hat Luffy and Pirate Hunter Zoro!

101
00:08:03.800 --> 00:08:06.170
So he broke out of the prison...

102
00:08:06.170 --> 00:08:10.260
This is Warden Babanuki in Udon.

103
00:08:10.590 --> 00:08:12.970
So, all is well.

104
00:08:18.480 --> 00:08:21.310
Tonight, we're celebrating the Golden Festival!

105
00:08:21.690 --> 00:08:25.280
So catch them as a gift for me!

106
00:08:26.780 --> 00:08:28.820
Hey, Queen!

107
00:08:28.820 --> 00:08:31.660
What's the prize for bringing them to you?

108
00:08:31.660 --> 00:08:36.290
Well, it just so happens
there's someone I want to axe...

109
00:08:38.830 --> 00:08:41.040
from the Soaring Six!

110
00:09:08.860 --> 00:09:14.280
Whoever catches these rats
for me can have the vacant spot!

111
00:09:20.710 --> 00:09:22.250
The Soaring Six, huh?

112
00:09:22.250 --> 00:09:25.290
Now that's my kind of reward!

113
00:09:27.840 --> 00:09:29.760
That spot is as good as mine!

114
00:09:32.510 --> 00:09:34.350
Apoo!

115
00:09:38.810 --> 00:09:40.890
That must be Kaido's castle back there!

116
00:09:40.890 --> 00:09:43.440
Let's clear a path and get inside!

117
00:09:43.440 --> 00:09:44.310
Sure!

118
00:09:59.330 --> 00:10:02.040
These guys seem like a real pain!

119
00:10:02.040 --> 00:10:03.210
What's their deal?

120
00:10:03.540 --> 00:10:07.040
They must be the ones that ate SMILE fruits!

121
00:10:24.400 --> 00:10:27.400
Check out my battle music!

122
00:10:27.400 --> 00:10:28.230
Scratch!

123
00:10:28.940 --> 00:10:29.610
Bop!

124
00:10:38.160 --> 00:10:38.780
Luffy!

125
00:10:39.200 --> 00:10:40.950
What the...?! Something punched me?!

126
00:10:46.170 --> 00:10:49.420
That guy was in an alliance with Jaggy's crew...

127
00:10:51.630 --> 00:10:52.720
Slash!

128
00:10:54.680 --> 00:10:55.430
Zoro!

129
00:10:55.430 --> 00:10:56.800
I got cut?!

130
00:11:00.010 --> 00:11:02.270
But he doesn't have a blade!

131
00:11:02.270 --> 00:11:04.480
I didn't see an attack either...!

132
00:11:05.600 --> 00:11:07.610
What kind of ability does he have?

133
00:11:12.280 --> 00:11:13.190
Boom!

134
00:11:16.820 --> 00:11:17.780
Luffy!

135
00:11:17.780 --> 00:11:20.370
Ch-Ch-Ch-Ch... Check it out!

136
00:11:21.990 --> 00:11:24.500
Whoa, whoa, gimme a break!

137
00:11:24.500 --> 00:11:26.170
That was too easy!

138
00:11:32.760 --> 00:11:35.050
It's no use! We gotta get out of here!

139
00:11:35.050 --> 00:11:36.760
Hey, you guys!

140
00:11:36.760 --> 00:11:40.510
Don't let them get away!

141
00:11:40.510 --> 00:11:45.480
If you want that spot in
the Soaring Six, you gotta work for it!

142
00:11:46.890 --> 00:11:49.400
If we take a bad beating here...

143
00:11:53.780 --> 00:11:56.280
we won't be able to knock out Kaido!

144
00:11:56.280 --> 00:11:59.030
As expected, it's not just their numbers.

145
00:11:59.990 --> 00:12:02.080
They're pretty tough!

146
00:12:02.080 --> 00:12:04.500
Soaring Six, here I come!

147
00:12:10.080 --> 00:12:11.170
Sorry.

148
00:12:11.170 --> 00:12:12.800
I'm all good now.

149
00:12:13.340 --> 00:12:14.920
Of course you are.

150
00:12:14.920 --> 00:12:17.840
Guess these disguises are kinda pointless now.

151
00:12:17.840 --> 00:12:19.130
You're right.

152
00:12:19.130 --> 00:12:21.100
It's hard to fight in them, too.

153
00:12:21.100 --> 00:12:22.970
Alright!

154
00:12:25.100 --> 00:12:28.190
We're done hiding! Let's
hurry up and break through!

155
00:12:28.730 --> 00:12:30.400
Right!

156
00:12:30.850 --> 00:12:32.310
It's no use.

157
00:12:32.310 --> 00:12:35.610
You guys are in my range.

158
00:12:35.610 --> 00:12:36.860
Check it out!

159
00:12:37.650 --> 00:12:39.110
What can we do?

160
00:12:39.860 --> 00:12:40.740
Scratch!

161
00:12:45.290 --> 00:12:46.580
Don't do it, Kid!

162
00:12:46.580 --> 00:12:48.580
You'll blow our cover, too!

163
00:13:00.680 --> 00:13:03.180
I don't give a damn!

164
00:13:08.930 --> 00:13:12.900
That double-crossing son of a bitch...!

165
00:13:14.650 --> 00:13:18.360
Everything is all his fault!

166
00:13:23.320 --> 00:13:25.910
Go to hell, Apoo!

167
00:13:25.910 --> 00:13:27.370
Kid!

168
00:13:27.700 --> 00:13:29.830
Punk...

169
00:13:35.880 --> 00:13:38.260
Gibson!

170
00:13:52.270 --> 00:13:54.270
Oh, Jaggy!

171
00:13:54.270 --> 00:13:55.690
That dummy!

172
00:13:59.150 --> 00:14:00.570
Apoo!

173
00:14:00.570 --> 00:14:02.950
Hey, that guy's an impostor!

174
00:14:16.630 --> 00:14:19.510
What?!

175
00:14:19.840 --> 00:14:21.300
Don't tell me...!

176
00:14:21.300 --> 00:14:22.420
Is that...?!

177
00:14:27.050 --> 00:14:30.470
It's Captain Kid!

178
00:14:34.850 --> 00:14:37.770
What the hell is Kid doing here?

179
00:14:37.770 --> 00:14:40.690
He's supposed to be locked up in Udon, too!

180
00:14:40.690 --> 00:14:45.360
You better have a damn good
explanation for this, Babanuki!

181
00:14:56.960 --> 00:15:01.170
You were so eager to form an alliance...

182
00:15:03.050 --> 00:15:04.630
Back then...

183
00:15:04.760 --> 00:15:07.390
I should've put it together!

184
00:15:10.510 --> 00:15:14.270
You were already one of Kaido's informants!

185
00:15:14.270 --> 00:15:18.060
Kaido knew every move that we made...

186
00:15:18.690 --> 00:15:22.150
because you were reporting to him, right?!

187
00:15:25.820 --> 00:15:28.120
You're just a kid after all!

188
00:15:28.120 --> 00:15:29.160
What?!

189
00:15:29.160 --> 00:15:35.080
Did you think our alliance was strong enough
to take down one of the Four Emperors?!

190
00:15:35.080 --> 00:15:36.920
Get real!

191
00:15:39.590 --> 00:15:42.170
After all, when have you ever heard...

192
00:15:42.170 --> 00:15:45.470
of a pirate alliance having a happy ending?!

193
00:15:45.470 --> 00:15:46.380
Scratch!

194
00:15:47.180 --> 00:15:49.220
Slash!

