401
00:21:55.630 --> 00:21:57.130
I see.

402
00:21:57.130 --> 00:22:00.130
The blueprints for the mansion were quite old.

403
00:22:00.130 --> 00:22:02.590
It is no surprise there have been additions.

404
00:22:02.590 --> 00:22:08.430
Building: "Sweet Entanglement"

405
00:22:03.260 --> 00:22:08.430
But it is far too conspicuous
for 2,000 soldiers to cross such a bridge!

406
00:22:11.270 --> 00:22:13.520
Hey, Kin'emon...

407
00:22:15.480 --> 00:22:18.440
Is... Is... Is...

408
00:22:18.440 --> 00:22:22.280
Is that a pleasure hall I see over there?!

409
00:22:22.280 --> 00:22:27.580
This pleasure hall is owned by
Black Maria, one of the Soaring Six.

410
00:22:32.910 --> 00:22:36.710
I bet there are tons of lovely ladies in there!

411
00:22:36.710 --> 00:22:38.590
Oh, Sanji!

412
00:22:39.130 --> 00:22:41.920
Wait, Sir Sanji!

413
00:22:43.130 --> 00:22:45.760
It's like he's being sucked in!

414
00:22:46.300 --> 00:22:48.930
We're gonna sneak in, too!

415
00:22:48.930 --> 00:22:52.560
We shall form a search team
for Lord Momonosuke!

416
00:22:52.560 --> 00:22:55.270
You've been super worried about him!

417
00:22:55.650 --> 00:22:57.060
Just admit it!

418
00:23:03.360 --> 00:23:06.410
Just leave Momo's rescue to us!

419
00:23:08.120 --> 00:23:12.000
That way you guys can focus on the fight!

420
00:23:12.330 --> 00:23:15.620
Lady Nami! Lady Carrot! Shinobu!

421
00:23:18.590 --> 00:23:20.710
You have my utmost gratitude!

422
00:23:20.710 --> 00:23:22.710
In truth, it has been weighing on me!

423
00:23:23.380 --> 00:23:24.630
I am counting on you!

424
00:23:28.430 --> 00:23:31.220
Someone's coming out of the pleasure hall!

425
00:23:33.270 --> 00:23:34.180
Is that...?

426
00:23:37.310 --> 00:23:39.980
Guess he didn't find any girls...

427
00:23:41.730 --> 00:23:46.280
After hearing the commotion
that Luffy and the others created,

428
00:23:46.280 --> 00:23:50.660
almost all of Kaido and Orochi's
subordinates have left the pleasure hall...

429
00:23:52.700 --> 00:23:54.200
Invaders!

430
00:23:54.200 --> 00:23:55.830
Catch them!

431
00:23:55.830 --> 00:23:57.210
Take them down!

432
00:24:10.470 --> 00:24:11.640
It's Killer!

433
00:24:14.470 --> 00:24:16.980
Hey! Hey! Hey!

434
00:24:17.440 --> 00:24:18.900
Yo! Yo!

435
00:24:18.900 --> 00:24:21.150
What's taking so long?

436
00:24:21.150 --> 00:24:23.610
That guy's not that strong!

437
00:24:25.320 --> 00:24:27.360
Did you guys know?

438
00:24:27.360 --> 00:24:29.950
Killer ate a defective SMILE fruit,

439
00:24:29.950 --> 00:24:34.370
and became a Pleasure!

440
00:24:36.410 --> 00:24:38.500
Hey, Killer!

441
00:24:38.500 --> 00:24:43.130
If you eat this, I'll give you
a chance to save your captain!

442
00:24:49.220 --> 00:24:51.180
What the hell's so funny?!

443
00:24:53.600 --> 00:24:55.890
You bastards!

444
00:25:02.810 --> 00:25:07.150
I'll send everyone who laughs at you to hell!

445
00:25:07.940 --> 00:25:09.030
That so?

446
00:25:11.780 --> 00:25:13.830
Hey, Jaggy!

447
00:25:13.830 --> 00:25:15.950
Don't cause any more trouble!

448
00:25:19.830 --> 00:25:23.330
So they broke out of Udon's prison...

449
00:25:23.330 --> 00:25:24.670
Should we go after them?

450
00:25:24.670 --> 00:25:26.550
Wouldn't hurt to get the credit...

451
00:25:26.960 --> 00:25:28.090
Forget it!

452
00:25:28.090 --> 00:25:29.920
It's just a few rats.

453
00:25:30.430 --> 00:25:33.970
Focus on finding Yamato for me instead!

454
00:25:33.970 --> 00:25:36.600
That's a much bigger deal.

455
00:25:37.270 --> 00:25:39.480
Do not let Sasaki beat us to the punch!

456
00:25:39.480 --> 00:25:40.480
Yes, sir!

457
00:25:44.440 --> 00:25:47.400
What's the holdup?! Ice these rejects, yo!

458
00:25:47.400 --> 00:25:50.200
Put 'em in a grave six feet below!

459
00:25:52.110 --> 00:25:53.160
In any case...

460
00:25:53.910 --> 00:25:56.660
I can't believe what Queen said...

461
00:26:00.040 --> 00:26:02.040
I've been wanting...

462
00:26:04.750 --> 00:26:06.630
to kill someone myself.

463
00:26:09.210 --> 00:26:12.050
If the women left, the men weren't far behind.

464
00:26:12.590 --> 00:26:14.340
It appears we can cross after all!

465
00:26:15.800 --> 00:26:18.430
Live floor infiltration team, good luck!

466
00:26:18.430 --> 00:26:19.930
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

467
00:26:21.020 --> 00:26:23.100
Nice! That's the spirit, guys!

468
00:26:23.810 --> 00:26:25.690
The rest of you, follow me!

469
00:26:25.690 --> 00:26:28.190
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

470
00:26:29.860 --> 00:26:32.650
Gunner and driver Usopp,

471
00:26:32.650 --> 00:26:38.080
move Brachio-Tank 5 ahead slowly,
matching speed with the infantry!

472
00:26:38.740 --> 00:26:42.460
Roger that, tank commander Chopper!

473
00:26:42.790 --> 00:26:44.290
Proceeding nice and slow!

474
00:26:48.500 --> 00:26:53.340
Keep an eye on the windows
of the pleasure hall just in case!

475
00:26:53.340 --> 00:26:54.340
Leave it to me!

476
00:26:56.300 --> 00:26:58.810
If you should see a silhouette…

477
00:26:59.560 --> 00:27:00.720
Kin'emon!

478
00:27:00.720 --> 00:27:03.060
What's all that racket outside?

479
00:27:04.100 --> 00:27:06.400
Everyone, into the water!

480
00:27:23.120 --> 00:27:24.080
What?!

481
00:27:37.390 --> 00:27:42.470
<b>The Falls

Outside

of Wano</b>

482
00:27:44.020 --> 00:27:46.020
Let's go, Brothers and Sisters!

483
00:27:46.020 --> 00:27:47.900
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

484
00:27:47.900 --> 00:27:49.560
King...

485
00:27:49.560 --> 00:27:53.320
I'll get even with that bastard
if it's the lickety last thing I do!

486
00:27:53.320 --> 00:27:55.450
Climb all the way to the top!

487
00:27:55.450 --> 00:27:57.950
But why the hell is this the only way in?!

488
00:27:57.950 --> 00:27:59.820
It's absolutely absurd!

489
00:28:00.160 --> 00:28:05.710
No, what's absurd is the Big Mom Pirates
allying with the Beast Pirates!

490
00:28:05.710 --> 00:28:08.330
It has to be a joke!

491
00:28:08.330 --> 00:28:10.250
What is Mama thinking?!

492
00:28:10.250 --> 00:28:12.460
Mama's made her decision!

493
00:28:12.460 --> 00:28:14.710
Forget about the alliance!

494
00:28:14.710 --> 00:28:17.680
Remember the reason we actually came!

495
00:28:17.680 --> 00:28:18.840
You're right!

496
00:28:18.840 --> 00:28:23.350
In order to restore our reputation,
we need to find Straw Hat, kill him...

497
00:28:23.350 --> 00:28:26.310
...and display his head for the world to see!

498
00:28:27.310 --> 00:28:28.940
How barbaric!

499
00:28:28.940 --> 00:28:30.900
More importantly...

500
00:28:31.480 --> 00:28:35.610
I can become Kaido's new favorite!

501
00:28:35.610 --> 00:28:37.570
Screw you, Flampe!

502
00:28:37.570 --> 00:28:39.360
We made it!

503
00:28:39.990 --> 00:28:41.030
Wano!

504
00:28:41.030 --> 00:28:43.580
We don't know what's out there!

505
00:28:43.580 --> 00:28:44.870
Prepare to fight!

506
00:28:46.500 --> 00:28:48.210
Don't drop your guard!

507
00:28:48.210 --> 00:28:52.500
Last time, at this very place, that damn King...

508
00:28:54.210 --> 00:28:55.090
That's...!

